{"tid":2021752,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"陳健波早半小時坐上主席台 場內外有大批黨衛軍及保安看守","createTime":"2020-05-18T02:34:13.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-18T02:45:17.000Z","uid":21470,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"d47ace905207003198953d592f39f14d6da14ab8","tid":2021752,"uid":21470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-18T02:34:13.000Z","msg":"立法會內會早上11時選主席 陳健波早半小時坐上主席台<br />\n18.05.2020 10:30<br />\n<br />\n立法會內務委員會早上11時將開會舉行主席選舉，被立法會主席梁君彥指派，主持選舉的陳健波，在開會前大約半小時，已經坐上主席台，會議室內外都有保安看守。大批機動部隊警員在立法會大樓附近巡邏戒備。<br />\n<br />\n立法會主席梁君彥上星期宣布引用外間法律意見，根據《議事規則》第92條，指派財委會主席陳健波，主持內會主席選舉，期間不會處理規程問題。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=1288243&amp;csid=261_341\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2FPage%2FZH-TW%2Fnewsdetail.aspx%3FItemId%3D1288243%26csid%3D261_341&d=bavYdQ8E6vkyiKAGb1dQCfMFbVPULjdiAdi6tpyrPMY%3D&h=2e5115b6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=1288243&amp;csid=261_341</a>"},{"pid":"31af54e09595e37d3bd9bddfd3b793fbdf59a853","tid":2021752,"uid":49018,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-18T02:41:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />啲保安真係賤過狗"},{"pid":"fbe212235dde14c015073ce734febbea363e18a0","tid":2021752,"uid":9160,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"31af54e09595e37d3bd9bddfd3b793fbdf59a853","tid":2021752,"uid":49018,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-18T02:41:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />啲保安真係賤過狗"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-18T02:42:02.000Z","msg":"本來就係狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a6159732d40a8e454548c7a79cae012d957f7918","tid":2021752,"uid":156096,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"31af54e09595e37d3bd9bddfd3b793fbd